{
  "texts": [
    "METHODOLOGY A.",
    "Problem DefinitionWhen applying the current Graph RAG to automotive fault knowledge management, two major challenges emerge.",
    "The first challenge is the difficulty in adapting to existing knowledge graphs.",
    "As previously mentioned, the current Graph RAG is based on the SP method.",
    "It can be considered that executable queries can be generated without high-cost training, which is generally needed [10], as the same LLM is utilized both for converting a user query q from the natural language space to a query q for KG databases in logical symbol space, as well as for constructing KGs from documents."
  ]
}